                    <h2 class="header">Physical Health</h2>

                    <p class="impact-text">

                        Drug abuse can cause physical effects such as organ damage, physical dependence, and increased
                        risk of health problems. It can also impair judgment and coordination, and increase the risk of
                        mental health disorders.

                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

