                    <h2 class="header">Mental Health</h2>

                    <p class="impact-text">

                        Drug abuse can cause mental and emotional problems such as depression, anxiety, psychosis, and
                        cognitive impairment. It can worsen existing mental health issues and impair cognitive function.

                    </p>

                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6 shown">

